---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About — Ohad Israeli">
  <section class="intro">
    <p class="signature">$ cat about.md</p>
    <h1>About</h1>
  </section>

  <div class="prose">
    <p>
      I'm Ohad — a Senior Solutions Engineer Team Leader at
      <a href="https://www.confluent.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Confluent</a>,
      based in Israel. I lead a team of solutions engineers and spend my days helping
      organizations design, build, and run real-time data-streaming systems on
      Apache Kafka.
    </p>

    <p>
      My path to streaming ran through the rest of the data stack. I started out at
      <strong>Oracle</strong> as an enterprise architect and principal sales
      consultant, leading technical sales across mobile, finance, shipping, and
      telecom. From there I moved to <strong>Redis Labs</strong> as a solution
      architect, working on in-memory data and search, before joining
      <strong>Confluent</strong> — first as a staff solutions engineer, now leading
      the team. Fifteen-plus years in, the common thread has always been the same:
      moving data well, at scale, under real-world constraints.
    </p>

    <h2>What I work on</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Data streaming &amp; <strong>Apache Kafka</strong> — event-driven architectures, stream processing</li>
      <li>Distributed systems and the trade-offs that come with them</li>
      <li>Solutions architecture across the data infrastructure stack</li>
      <li>In-memory data &amp; search (Redis), and enterprise data platforms (Oracle)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>About this site</h2>
    <p>
      Each project I work on gets its own article under
      <a href="/projects">/projects</a>. When a project has real code behind it, it
      lives in its own repository and the article links straight to it; smaller
      experiments live entirely in the write-up.
    </p>

    <h2>Elsewhere</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>LinkedIn — <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/israeliohad/" target="_blank" rel="me noopener">in/israeliohad</a></li>
      <li>GitHub — <a href="https://github.com/ohad-israeli" target="_blank" rel="me noopener">github.com/ohad-israeli</a></li>
      <li>RSS — <a href="/rss.xml">subscribe to new projects</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
